  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat",
    "Add the onion and garlic and saute until the onion is translucent",
    "Add the smoked paprika and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the fernbrake, vegetable broth, potatoes, carrots, salt, and black pepper",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired",
    "Let the stew cool slightly before serving",
    "Serve with crusty bread or over rice"
